# Articles & MDX components

## New article checklist

1. Create `src/content/articles/<slug>.mdx` with frontmatter (`title`, `description`, `date`, `draft`, `tags`)
2. Import existing components from `src/components/articles/` — reuse before creating new ones
3. Set `draft: false` when ready for production (excluded from build/sitemap/RSS when `true`)
4. Add `relatedArticles` / topic hub slug arrays on related talks/work/topics
5. Browser-test `/articles/<slug>/`

## Component patterns

- React (`.tsx`) with semantic token classes
- Scroll reveal: wrap in `article-reveal`; stagger children with nested `article-stagger` > `article-stagger-item`
- **Do not** put `article-reveal` and `article-stagger` on the same element without the nested-child pattern (causes invisible content)

## Layout & SEO

`ArticleLayout.astro`: ToC, author bio, related articles, `BlogPosting` + `BreadcrumbList` schema. Title: `{title} | Rafael Roman`.

After publishing, update relevant `/topics/*` hub `relatedArticles` if the article fits a cluster.
